\"><em>i</em></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;&mdash; for what number of students the first news they\'ve learned over the&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>m</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;days in question, was the news number&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">. The number of the news is the number of the day on which it can be learned. The days are numbered starting from one in the order in which they are given in the input file. Don\'t output&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>res</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">0</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">.</span></p>','3 4\n2 3 1\n1 2 3 4\n1 2 3 4\n\n8 6\n7 6 4 2 3 5 5 7\n10 4 3 8 9 1\n1 1 1 2 2 2','1\n1\n1\n0\n\n1\n1\n1\n2\n1\n1','0','<p>dp dsu</p>','B 45','2016-07-21 13:59:34',2,256,'Y',NULL,0,0),(1032,'导演撰名','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">保罗是一个导演，他知道去一个男主角的名字有多么重要。他列了一张有n个名和n个姓的表库。他可以接受任何名字和姓的匹配。他需要的全名显示格式如：\"<span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\"><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>Name</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 14.4375px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>Surname</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 14.4375px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>Name</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 14.4375px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>Surname</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 14.4375px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">...</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>Name</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 14.4375px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>n</em></span></span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 19.25px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>Surname</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 14.4375px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>n</em></span></span></span>\", i.e. 所有全名间用&ldquo;，&rdquo;分割，名和姓之间空格分割。 所有名和姓都按照ASCII字母顺序选取，且都只能选择一次。</p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输入第一行为一个正整数&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">) &mdash; 代表姓的数量和名的数量。接下来n行是名，在接下来n行是姓。输入保证2n个名和姓都不同。每一个名和姓都非空且长度不超过10的拉丁字母。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">名和姓的</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第一个字母是大写，其余字母都小写。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出一行，按照全名的输出格式显示，最后一个名字后面没有&ldquo;，&rdquo;。</span></p>','4\nAnn\nAnna\nSabrina\nJohn\nPetrov\nIvanova\nStoltz\nAbacaba\n','Ann Abacaba, Anna Ivanova, John Petrov, Sabrina Stoltz','0','<p>constructive algorithms、greedy</p>','','2016-07-21 15:10:59',2,256,'N',1,1,0),(10003,'斑马和老虎','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">有一次法鲁西要带m头斑马和m头老虎尽快的过河。船只能载n头动物。在一个地方（岸的任意一边或船上）老虎的数量如果大于斑马的数量，那么老虎会吃了斑马，法鲁西会很难过</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;。当法鲁西划船过河时，如果船上没有动物，那么他会寂寞也会很难过。当船抵达河岸的时候，所有的动物先同时下船，然后法鲁西再选一些动物上船。</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;留下的动物不能被吃。所有如果要法鲁西不难过，他最少需要划船几次？&nbsp;</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输入第一行两个空格分隔的正整数</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>m</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>m</em>,&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">5</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">) &mdash; 代表一种动物的数量和船的容量。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">如果不能把动物都安全送上岸，或者法鲁西难过 输出-1；否则输出一个正整数，代表法鲁西需要过河的次数。</span></p>','第一个例子：\n3 2\n\n第二个例子：\n33 3','第一个例子：\n11\n\n第二个例子：\n-1','0','<p>greedy</p>','','2016-07-21 20:18:38',2,256,'N',1,2,0),(1033,'停车位','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">在城市里停车是个大问题。假设有一条&nbsp;</span><em style=\"color: #222222;\">L&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">米长的停车道，每辆车需要严格靠停车线右测平行停放。一个司机要停车必须保证离后排车的距离不小于</span><em style=\"color: #222222;\">b</em><span style=\"color: #222222;\">米，</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">离前排车的距离不小于</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>f</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">米（如果前排或后排没有车，车可以贴停车道的起始和末尾边停放）。给车道引入坐标值，车道起始点为0，末尾点为L。</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;每辆车驶入的时候总是寻找坐标值最小的可停放的点，如果没有可停放的点，那么车就驶离车道。</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;有时候有些车会离开停车位，那么这个位置就空出来可供其他车停放。车道上不能同时行驶两辆车，编写一个程序模拟停车位的使用过程。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第一行输入三个正整数&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>L</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>b</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>f</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">10&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>L</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100000,&thinsp;1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>b</em>,&thinsp;<em>f</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">)。第二行输入输入是一个正整数</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">) 表示对停车道的使用请求，每个请求的描述由接下来的n行输入表示，每行输入是两个正整数，第一个数字代表请求类型，如果是1，表示车驶入停车位，车的长度由第二个数字表示；第一个数字如果是2，表示有车驶离条车道，第二个数字表示一个请求序号，这个请求保证是之前发生过的车驶入请求。车的长度为从</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">1</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;到&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">1000</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">的正整数。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出的内容对应的是所有类型为1的车驶入车道请求，输出一行-1 如果驶入的车找不到停车点，除此之外输出车尾部停的坐标点的值。</span></p>','第一个例子：\n30 1 2\n6\n1 5\n1 4\n1 5\n2 2\n1 5\n1 4\n第二个例子：\n30 1 1\n6\n1 5\n1 4\n1 5\n2 2\n1 5\n1 4\n第三个例子：\n10 1 1\n1\n1 12','第一个例子：\n0\n6\n11\n17\n23\n第二个例子：\n0\n6\n11\n17\n6\n第三个例子：\n-1','0','<p>data structures、implementation</p>','','2016-07-21 22:22:56',2,256,'N',1,1,0),(10005,'熊和监狱','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">有一个&nbsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;<em>n&nbsp;</em>的网格划分的监狱牢房，每个牢房要么是空的用&ldquo;.&rdquo;表示，要么被封了用&ldquo;X&rdquo;表示。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">两个空的紧挨着（有一边重合）的牢房是相连的。两个牢房&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">(<em>r</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>,&thinsp;<em>c</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>)</span>&nbsp;(第&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>r</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span></span>&nbsp;行第and column&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>c</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span></span>列） 和&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">(<em>r</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>,&thinsp;<em>c</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>)</span>&nbsp;是联通的如果存在一串空的牢房从<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">(<em>r</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>,&thinsp;<em>c</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>)</span>开始， 到&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">(<em>r</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>,&thinsp;<em>c</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>)</span>结束，任意两个连续的牢房是相连的。相连的块就是一组空的牢房其中任意两个牢房是联通的。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">有一只大灰熊，他能摧毁任何牢房的墙，简单讲，你能选择一个<em>k</em>&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;<em>k</em><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">的牢房区域，熊能打通这个牢房区域。但是你只有一次使用它的机会。被选中的</span><em>k</em>&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;<em>k</em><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">区域一定是在整个网格中，也有可能熊不需要打通任何牢房如果所有牢房已经都是空的。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">你喜欢大的联通区域，请让熊帮你打开最大的联通区域。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第一行输入两个正整数&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>k</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;500</span>)&nbsp;&mdash; 代表整个正方网格的边长大小和熊要打通的正方区域边长大小。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">接下来n行，每一行n个字符，每个字符要么是<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">\'</span><span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\">.</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">\'代表空的牢房，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">要么是</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">&nbsp;\'</span><span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\">X</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">\' 代表被封的牢房。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出一个正整数，</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">代表熊打通</span><em>k</em>&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;<em>k&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">个牢房后能形成的最大联通区域里牢房的数量。</span></p>','5 2\n..XXX\nXX.XX\nX.XXX\nX...X\nXXXX.','10','0','<p><span style=\"color: #222222;\">比如熊能打通的区域大小是&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">2&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;2</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">. 打通下图中红色边框的牢房，那么就能得到10个标记为蓝色的联通牢房</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"/data/10005/10005.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>dfs and similar、dsu、implementation</p>','','2016-07-21 23:39:20',3,256,'N',3,3,0),(1034,'LRU','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">While creating high loaded systems one should pay a special attention to caching. This problem will be about one of the most popular caching algorithms called LRU (Least Recently Used).</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Suppose the cache may store no more than&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;objects. At the beginning of the workflow the cache is empty. When some object is queried we check if it is present in the cache and move it here if it\'s not. If there are more than&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;objects in the cache after this, the least recently used one should be removed. In other words, we remove the object that has the smallest time of the last query.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Consider there are&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;videos being stored on the server, all of the same size. Cache can store no more than&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;videos and caching algorithm described above is applied. We know that any time a user enters the server he pick the video&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>i</em></span>&nbsp;with probability&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>. The choice of the video is independent to any events before.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The goal of this problem is to count for each of the videos the probability it will be present in the cache after&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">100</span></span>&nbsp;queries.</p>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The first line of the input contains two integers&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>k</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;20</span>)&nbsp;&mdash; the number of videos and the size of the cache respectively. Next line contains&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;real numbers&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">0&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;1</span>), each of them is given with no more than two digits after decimal point.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">It\'s guaranteed that the sum of all&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>&nbsp;is equal to&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1</span>.</p>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\">Print&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;real numbers, the&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\"><em>i</em></span>-th of them should be equal to the probability that the&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\"><em>i</em></span>-th video will be present in the cache after&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">100</span></span>&nbsp;queries. You answer will be considered correct if its absolute or relative error does not exceed&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">&thinsp;-&thinsp;6</span></span>.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">Namely: let\'s assume that your answer is&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><em>a</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">, and the answer of the jury is&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 1.4em;\"><em>b</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em;\">. The checker program will consider your answer correct, &nbsp; if &nbsp;|a-b|/max(1,b) &lt;= &nbsp;</span>10<span class=\"upper-index\">-6</span></p>','sample 1:\n3 1\n0.3 0.2 0.5\n\nsample 2:\n2 1\n0.0 1.0\n\nsample 3:\n3 2\n0.3 0.2 0.5\n\nsample 4:\n3 3\n0.2 0.3 0.5','sample1: 0.3 0.2 0.5\nsample2: 0.0 1.0 \nsample3: 0.675 0.4857142857142857 0.8392857142857143\nsample4: 1.0 1.0 1.0 ','1','<p>bitmasks、dp、probabilityes</p>','','2016-07-22 11:44:27',2,256,'Y',NULL,0,0),(1035,'子集','<div class=\"input-specification\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #222222;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #222222;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em !important; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">程序员璐璐最近开始学习数据结构。老师给了她一个任务，在一组固定数量的数字集合里找出只出现一次的最大的数。请帮璐璐找到这个数。</p>\n</div>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第一行包含两个正整数&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">5</span>,&thinsp;1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>k</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em></span>) &mdash; 分别代表数组里所有元素的个数，和子集里元素的个数。&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">接下来n行：第&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>i</em></span>-th 行包含一个正整数 <span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">&thinsp;-&thinsp;10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">9</span>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">9</span></span>).</p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em>&ndash;<em>k</em>&thinsp;+&thinsp;1</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;个数，每个数一行: 第&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">-th 行的数表示子集</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em>&thinsp;+&thinsp;1</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;&hellip;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em>&thinsp;+&thinsp;<em>k</em>&thinsp;-&thinsp;1</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">里最大的一个数，且这个数只出现一次。如果不存这个数，输出 \"</span><span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">Nothing</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">\"。</span></p>','第一个例子：\n5 3\n1\n2\n2\n3\n3\n第二个例子：\n6 4\n3\n3\n3\n4\n4\n2','第一个例子：\n1\n3\n2\n\n第二个例子：\n4\nNothing\n3','0','<p>data structures、implementation</p>','','2016-07-22 15:19:38',1,256,'N',2,2,0),(1036,'移动点','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">Anton 和 Dasha 喜欢玩方格纸。Vova 推荐他们玩一种称之为&ldquo;dot&rdquo;的新游戏，规则如下：</p>\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em;\">方格纸上画了一个坐标系。一个点初始位置为&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">(<em>x</em>,&thinsp;<em>y</em>)</span>.</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em;\">每一步点的移动是由向量控制的，向量在游戏中是给定的，每个玩家每局游戏还可以使用一次将点对着直线 y=x对称反射的操作。</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em;\">Anton 和&nbsp;Dasha 每次轮流。Anton 先手。</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1em;\">当玩家把点移动到一个坐标点相对原点距离大于d的时候就输了。</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">请帮助他们找到胜利者。</p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第一行输入4个正整数&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>x</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>y</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>d</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">&thinsp;-&thinsp;200&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>x</em>,&thinsp;<em>y</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;200,&thinsp;1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>d</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;200,&thinsp;1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;20</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">) &mdash; 点的初始坐标，向量的数量和判断游戏胜负的距离。输入保证初始点相对原点的距离大于d。接下来n行是两个非负正整数</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;和&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>y</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">0&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span>,&thinsp;<em>y</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;200</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">) &mdash; 代表玩家可以选择的移动向量，输入保证所有向量非0且都是不同的。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">假设两个玩家的玩法没有任何失误，输出 \"</span><span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">Anton</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">\",如果Anton赢得比赛，反之输出\"</span><span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">Dasha</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">\"&nbsp;。</span></p>','第一个例子：\n0 0 2 3\n1 1\n1 2\n\n第二个例子：\n0 0 2 4\n1 1\n1 2','第一个例子：\nAnton\n\n第二个例子：\nDasha','0','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第一个例子, Anton 先手将点移动到 (1,2), Dasha 就输了. 第二个例子，Dasha在第二步的时候能将点移动到 (2，3), Anton 就输了, 这个时候Antona唯一的选择是对着直线&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>y</em>&thinsp;=&thinsp;<em>x </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">做映射， Dasha 接下来也可以用相同的做法将点再移回(2，3)。</span></p>\n<p>dp、games</p>','','2016-07-22 17:03:50',3,256,'N',1,1,0),(1037,'哈利波特和分院帽','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em !important; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">我们知道<span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.02px;\">霍格沃兹魔法学校有四个学院</span><span style=\"font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">: Gryffindor, Hufflepuff, Ravenclaw 和 Slytherin. 魔法学员会在第一年被分到四个不同学院。学生按项目字母顺序被安排带上分院帽，结果沉思后，帽子会庄严宣布学生要进入的学院名&nbsp;。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">帽子会根据学生的综合素质: 勇敢和高尚的学生被送到Gryffindor, 聪明和精明的学生被送到Ravenclaw, 坚韧和诚实的学生被送到Hufflepuff，奸诈和阴险的学生被送到Slytherin。然而，一年级学生Hermione Granger 十分担心接下来的分院过程，她研究的分院帽的分院机制，发现远比想象的要简单。如果该学生的亲戚已经在<span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.02px;\">霍格沃兹魔法学校学习，那么这个学生会被送到他亲戚所在学院。在极端情况，如果这些亲戚在不同学院学习或者像</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">Hermione父母那样不在学院学习，那么学生会被分派到当前被分派学员最少的学院，如果有几个学院拥有一样少的学员，那么这个学生可以从这些学院中挑一个自己想去的。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">Hermione 已经询问了名字顺序在她前面的所有学生的亲属所在学院，现在她和她的朋友Harry Potter 和 Ron Weasley 想推算出她能进那个学院。</p>\n</div>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第一行输入一个正整数&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10000</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">). 名字排名在Hermione前面的学生个数.第二行是由n个字符组成的字符串，如果第</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">-th个学生的所有亲属都在一个学院学习，那么第</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">-th 字符就是该学院名字的开头字母，否则</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">-th 字符就是</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;\"?\".</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出所有 Hermione 可能被送进的学院。学院名字排序根据开头字母顺序，每个名字占一行。&nbsp;</span></p>','第一个例子：\n11\nG????SS???H\n\n第二个例子：\n2\nH?','第一个例子：\nGryffindor\nRavenclaw\n\n第二个例子：\nGryffindor\nRavenclaw\nSlytherin','0','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">在第二个例子中，只有两个学生在 Hermione前面。第一个学生被送到了 Hufflepuff. 第二个学生从学员最少的学院中选择一个，分别为：Gryffindor, Slytherin and Ravenclaw. 如果他选择 Gryffindor, 那么Hermione 只能选择 Ravenclaw 或 Slytherin, 如果他选择Ravenclaw, 那么Hermione 将选择 Gryffindor 或 Slytherin, 如果他选择 Slytherin, 那么Hermione 将选择 Gryffindor 或 Ravenclaw. 最终，可能的情况会是1) in Gryffindor, 2) in Ravenclaw, 3) in Slytherin。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">brute force、dfs and similar、hashing</span></p>','','2016-07-23 01:53:52',2,256,'N',1,1,0),(1038,'僵尸脑生长','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em !important; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">关于僵尸脑子的研究有了新的进展。每个僵尸是由一个脑子生长出来的，之后脑子再进化成更复杂的结构。实际，只要僵尸吃一个脑子，就会长出一个新的脑子，新的脑子会和任意一个老的脑子通过一根脑连接器连在一起，形成一个新的脑网络。研究员想要监测僵尸脑延迟（任意两个脑子间最长需要的脑连接数），写一个程序模拟僵尸脑神经系统进化过程，计算每一阶段的脑延迟。</p>\n</div>','<p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #222222;\">第一行输入一个正整数，表示最终神经系统的脑子数</span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">2&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;200000</span>)。<span style=\"color: #222222;\">第二行输入开始是脑子的进化过程，根据每个脑子生长顺序给脑子编号</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">1,&thinsp;2,&thinsp;...,&thinsp;<em>n</em></span>&nbsp;(<span style=\"color: #222222;\">僵尸是由一个脑子开始进化的，第一个脑子是 1，顺序的后面生长出的脑子是</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">2,&thinsp;3,&thinsp;...,&thinsp;<em>n</em></span>&nbsp;)。 之后&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\"><em>n</em>&thinsp;-&thinsp;1</span>&nbsp;行，每一行一个正整数&nbsp;<em style=\"color: #222222;\">p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; color: #222222;\">k ,</span>表示第k个脑子加入脑神经，和它接入的脑子是<em style=\"color: #222222;\">p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; color: #222222;\">k，</span><span class=\"lower-index\"><em style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">p</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em; color: #222222; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">k</span><em>&nbsp;</em></span><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20.02px;\">&isin; </span><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">{1,2,...,k-1}。</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em>n</em>&thinsp;-&thinsp;1</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;个正整数，由空格分隔，每个正整数表示第k个脑子加入后，大脑延迟数的值，</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap; color: #222222; line-height: 19.6px;\"><em style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px;\">k</em><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">&thinsp;=&thinsp;2,&thinsp;3,&thinsp;...,&thinsp;</span></span><em><span style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17.5px;\">n</span></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></span></em></span></p>','6\n1\n2\n2\n1\n5','1 2 2 3 4','0','<p>trees</p>','','2016-07-23 14:24:22',2,256,'N',1,1,0),(10006,'航海最短距离','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">你有一个新工作，很有趣，你是船船长。你的第一个任务是将船从一个点移到另一个点，而且要花费最小的成本。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">众所周知，两点间最短的距离是连接两点的线段。很遗憾，有时两个点之间有一座岛，船不能直线行驶。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">你只能将船行驶到安全点上，安全点的定义为连接两个目标点的线段上的点或者是岛的边界。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">但你很幸运，你拥有一些聪明而强壮的工人能帮助你，他们能帮你以1英镑每单元距离的成本在海中行驶；能以2英镑每单元距离在岛上推着船（他们非常强壮）移动。钱会被所有工人评分，所以工人的数量不在考虑范围内。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">现在你有一张地图，你要花最少的费用完成航行，你从点(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>xStart</em></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>yStart</em></span>)开始，结束点为 (<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>xEnd</em></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>yEnd</em></span>)，两个点是不同的。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">岛是一个凸多边形形状，不存在2个以上的顶点在一条直线上，同样开始点和结束点不会在多边形内或边上，多边形的点会以逆时针的方向排序。</p>','<p>&nbsp;第一行输入4个正整数,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">xStart</em></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">yStart</em></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">xEnd</em></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">yEnd</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">&thinsp;-&thinsp;100&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">xStart</em>,&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">yStart</em>,&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">xEnd</em>,&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">yEnd</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100</span>). 第二行是一个正整数<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">n</em></span>, 代表多边形的顶点数(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">3&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;30</span>), 第三行输入是&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">n</em></span>&nbsp;对正整数&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">x</em></span>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">y&nbsp;</em></span>坐标点 (<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">&thinsp;-&thinsp;100&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">x</em>,&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">y</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100</span>), 所有的点两两不同。</p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出一个数，代表所花费的最小费用，该数精确到小数点后9位。</span></p>','第一个例子：\n1 7 6 7\n4\n4 2 4 12 3 12 3 2\n\n第二个例子：\n-1 0 2 0\n4\n0 0 1 0 1 1 0 1','第一个例子：\n6.000000000\n\n第二个例子：\n3.000000000','0','<p>geometry、shortest paths</p>','','2016-07-23 17:52:08',2,256,'N',1,4,0),(10007,'基因突变','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">科学家对奥林匹亚星球的基本生物基因做了深入的研究，发现该星球的生物基因可由前K个英文字母表示。对每组基因对<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em>,&thinsp;<em>j</em></span></span>&nbsp;&mdash; 表示两种基因元素相邻出现在基因里会引起致病基因的风险指数，<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>i</em></span>&nbsp;&mdash; 代表第一个基因元素的序号，&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>j</em></span>&nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">代表第二个基因元素的序号</span>. 基因元素 \'A\' 的序号是 1, \'B\' 的序号是 2 ，以此类推。 比如,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">3,&thinsp;2</span></span>&nbsp;代表基因片段 \'CB\' 的<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">. 生物的的</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数是所有相邻基因元素的致病风险指数的总和。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">科学家已经获得了一串基因，对这个基因做突变实验，突变的过程是移除其中的一些基因元素，突变会引起新的额外的致病风险。对每种移除的基因元素，科学家定义&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>t</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>&nbsp;&mdash; 表示移除所有基因元素&nbsp;<em>i</em>&nbsp;后增加的致病风险指数。比如,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>t</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">4</span></span>&nbsp;代表移除基因元素<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">\'D\'后增加的</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">科学家们想从一个基本基因中发现一些不同的基因，这些基因的<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数不高于</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>T</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">. 科学家门只使用上述基因突变的方式获取新基因。只要代表基因类型的字符组成的字符串是不同的，两种基因就不同，每个基因至少包含一个基因元素。</span></p>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第一行输入有三个正整数<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>N</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>N</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;200&thinsp;000</span>) &mdash; 代表基因字符串总长度,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>K</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>K</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;22</span>) &mdash; 基因元素种类的个数，&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>T</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>T</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;2&middot;10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">9</span></span>) &mdash; 允许的最大的致病风险指数。第二行输入生物的基因字串，由<em style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">K</em>各英文字母组成的长度为<em style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">N</em><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第三行是&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>K</em></span>&nbsp;个正整数&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>t</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>,&thinsp;<em>t</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>,&thinsp;...,&thinsp;<em>t</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>K</em></span></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>t</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>&nbsp;是移除所有种类为<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">-th 的基因元素后，增加的致病风险指数。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">接下来&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>K</em></span>&nbsp;行是一个矩阵，每个矩阵元素由<em style=\"font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em>,&thinsp;<em>j</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">表示。</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">第&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">-th 行有&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>K</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">&nbsp;可正整数. 第&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>j</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">-th 列第&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>i</em></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">-th 行的值代表（i,j）基因元素对的</span><span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数，矩阵不一定是对称矩阵。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">所有的输入都是正整数, 没有负数，所有的数除了<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>T</em></span>&nbsp;没有大于<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">10<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">9</span></span>的。输入保证计算得出的任何生物<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数小于</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">2<span class=\"upper-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;\">31</span></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">.</span></p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出满足</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">致病风险指数小于&nbsp;</span><em style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">T&nbsp;</em><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">的所有突变基因的个数。</span></p>','5 3 13\nBACAC\n4 1 2\n1 2 3\n2 3 4\n3 4 10','5','0','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">满足条件的所有的突变基因，括号里的值为致病风险指数</span><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">: BACAC (11), ACAC (10), BAA (5), B (6), AA (4)。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">bitmasks、dp、math</span></p>','','2016-07-24 15:30:24',3,256,'N',1,1,0),(1039,'城堡密码','<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em !important; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">凯尔在一座城堡前，进入城堡需要密码，这个密码有点特别。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1em !important; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">密码输入设备是一个&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">n</em></span>&nbsp;的长方形器件，有n个槽，从左到右标记为1到n。每个槽有ON 和 OFF 两个状态。初始状态都为OFF，凯尔只有把 第&nbsp;<em style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>-th,&nbsp;<em style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>-th,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">...</span>,&nbsp;<em style=\"font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 19.6px; white-space: nowrap;\">x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">k</span>-th 个位置的槽设为ON，其他槽为OFF&nbsp;。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">凯尔被给到一个数组&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">a</em><sub class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</sub></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">...</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">a</em><sub class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">l</em></sub></span>。每一步操作,他先挑选&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">i</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">i</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em style=\"font-style: italic;\">l</em></span>), 然后选择&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">a</em><sub class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em style=\"font-style: italic;\">i</em></sub></span>&nbsp;个连续的槽, 切换这些槽的状态 (i.e. ON<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">&thinsp;&rarr;&thinsp;</span>OFF, OFF<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">&thinsp;&rarr;&thinsp;</span>ON).</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.4em;\">凯尔只能通过上述的操作才能打开锁，请问他至少需要几步操作才能打开锁。</p>\n</div>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第一行输入3个正整数&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>l</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10000,&thinsp;1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>k</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10,&thinsp;1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>l</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;100</span>), 空格分隔。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第二行输入&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>k</em></span>&nbsp;个正整数<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span></span>, ...,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>k</em></span></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span>&thinsp;&lt;&thinsp;<em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">2</span>&thinsp;&lt;&thinsp;...&thinsp;&lt;&thinsp;<em>x</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>k</em></span>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em></span>),&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">空格分隔。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">第三行输入&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>l</em></span>&nbsp;个正整数&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\">1</span></span>, ...,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>l</em></span></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em></span>),<span style=\"line-height: 19.6px;\">空格分隔。</span>一些&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>a</em><span class=\"lower-index\" style=\"font-size: 13.125px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; bottom: -0.25em;\"><em>i</em></span></span>&nbsp;元素有可能重复。</p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">输出打开锁需要的最少的操作步骤，输出-1如果不可能打开锁。</span></p>','第一个例子：\n10 8 2\n1 2 3 5 6 7 8 9\n3 5\n\n第二个例子：\n3 2 1\n1 2\n3','第一个例子：\n2\n\n第二个例子：\n-1','0','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">第一个例子中，第一步: 选择 1st, 2nd, 3rd 个槽，切换状态；第二步，选择5th, 6th, 7th, 8th, 9th 个槽，切换状态。</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>bitmasks、dp、shortest path</p>','','2016-07-24 17:46:22',1,256,'N',1,1,0),(10008,'Evacuation','<p style=\"padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 1em !important;\">They\'ve screwed something up yet again... In one nuclear reactor of a research station an uncontrolled reaction is in progress and explosion which will destroy the whole station will happen soon.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The station is represented by a square&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em>&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;<em>n</em></span>&nbsp;divided into&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&times;&thinsp;1</span>&nbsp;blocks. Each block is either a reactor or a laboratory. There can be several reactors and exactly one of them will explode soon. The reactors can be considered impassable blocks, but one can move through laboratories. Between any two laboratories, which are in adjacent blocks, there is a corridor. Blocks are considered adjacent if they have a common edge.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In each laboratory there is some number of scientists and some number of rescue capsules. Once the scientist climbs into a capsule, he is considered to be saved. Each capsule has room for not more than one scientist.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The reactor, which is about to explode, is damaged and a toxic coolant trickles from it into the neighboring blocks. The block, which contains the reactor, is considered infected. Every minute the coolant spreads over the laboratories through corridors. If at some moment one of the blocks is infected, then the next minute all the neighboring laboratories also become infected. Once a lab is infected, all the scientists there that are not in rescue capsules die. The coolant does not spread through reactor blocks.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">There are exactly&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>t</em></span>&nbsp;minutes to the explosion. Any scientist in a minute can move down the corridor to the next lab, if it is not infected. On any corridor an unlimited number of scientists can simultaneously move in both directions. It is believed that the scientists inside a lab moves without consuming time. Moreover, any scientist could get into the rescue capsule instantly. It is also believed that any scientist at any given moment always has the time to perform their actions (move from the given laboratory into the next one, or climb into the rescue capsule) before the laboratory will be infected.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Find the maximum number of scientists who will be able to escape.</p>','<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">The first line contains two integers&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>t</em></span>&nbsp;(<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">2&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>n</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;10</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\">1&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;<em>t</em>&thinsp;&le;&thinsp;60</span>). Each of the next&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;lines contains&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;characters. These lines describe the scientists\' locations. Then exactly one empty line follows. Each of the next&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;more lines contains&nbsp;<span class=\"tex-span\" style=\"font-size: 17.5px; font-family: \'times new roman\', sans-serif; white-space: nowrap;\"><em>n</em></span>&nbsp;characters. These lines describe the rescue capsules\' locations.</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">In the description of the scientists\' and the rescue capsules\' locations the character \"<span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\">Y</span>\" stands for a properly functioning reactor, \"<span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\">Z</span>\" stands for the malfunctioning reactor. The reactors\' positions in both descriptions coincide. There is exactly one malfunctioning reactor on the station. The digits \"<span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\">0</span>\" - \"<span class=\"tex-font-style-tt\" style=\"font-size: 15.4px; font-family: \'courier new\', monospace;\">9</span>\" stand for the laboratories. In the description of the scientists\' locations those numbers stand for the number of scientists in the corresponding laboratories. In the rescue capsules\' descriptions they stand for the number of such capsules in each laboratory.</p>','<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.6px;\">Print a single number &mdash; the maximum number of scientists who will manage to save themselves.</span></p>','第一个例子：\n3 3\n1YZ\n1YY\n100\n\n0YZ\n0YY\n003\n\n第二个例子：\n4 4\nY110\n1Y1Z\n1Y0Y\n0100\n\nY001\n0Y0Z\n0Y0Y\n0005','第一个例子：\n2\n\n第二个例子：\n3','0','<p><span style=\"color: #222222;\">In the second sample the events could take place as follows:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222;\"><img src=\"/data/10008/10008.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p>flows、graphs、shortest paths</p>','','2016-07-25 00:48:10',1,256,'N',1,2,0);
